No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C37E65015A729806FA56F8F3E87DF839" pageId="5" pageNumber="198" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="8BDB368A5A729806FA56F8F3E87DF839" blockId="5.[1438,2646,1438,1979]" pageId="5" pageNumber="198">
<emphasis id="B910EA985A729806FA56F8F3E900F8C0" bold="true" box="[1441,1797,1872,1901]" pageId="5" pageNumber="198">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List (as 
<taxonomicName id="4C644D095A729806F5D3F8F3E80EF839" authorityName="Mivart" authorityYear="1867" class="Mammalia" family="Chrysochloridae" genus="Calcochloris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Afrosoricida" pageId="5" pageNumber="198" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Calcochloris</taxonomicName>
tytonas).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
